The paper proposes a new structure for the complex-valued autoencoder and develops a widely linear backpropagation algorithm. The paper also discusses the optimization of phase and amplitude information, which is relevant to machine learning and signal processing. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.SI (Signal and Image Processing).
